#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:571
msgid "Scripts"
msgstr "スクリプト"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:573
msgid ""
"The `scripts` field is used to define custom scripts associated with the "
"module."
msgstr "`scripts` フィールドは、モジュールに関連付けるカスタムスクリプトを定義するために使います。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:575
msgid "postadd script"
msgstr "postadd スクリプト"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:577
msgid ""
"The `postadd` script runs automatically after the module has been added. "
"When executed, the script's current working directory (cwd) is set to the"
" directory where the `moon.mod.json` file resides."
msgstr ""
"`postadd` スクリプトは、モジュールが追加された後に自動的に実行されます。実行時、スクリプトの現在の作業ディレクトリ（cwd）は "
"`moon.mod.json` ファイルがあるディレクトリに設定されます。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:583
msgid ""
"options(\n"
"  scripts: {\n"
"    \"postadd\": \"python3 build.py\",\n"
"  },\n"
")\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:592
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"scripts\": {\n"
"    \"postadd\": \"python3 build.py\"\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:603
msgid "\\[Experimental\\] Pre-build config script"
msgstr "\\[実験的\\] 事前ビルド設定スクリプト"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:606
msgid ""
"This feature is extremely experimental, and its API may change at any "
"time. This documentation reflects the implementation as of 2025-06-03."
msgstr "この機能は非常に実験的であり、API はいつでも変更される可能性があります。このドキュメントは 2025-06-03 時点の実装を反映しています。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:611
msgid ""
"Using this feature may execute arbitrary code in your computer. Please "
"use with caution and only with trusted dependencies."
msgstr "この機能を使うと、コンピュータ上で任意のコードが実行される可能性があります。注意して使用し、信頼できる依存関係に対してのみ使ってください。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:615
msgid ""
"The pre-build config script is added in order to aid native target "
"programming. To use such script, add your script in your `moon.mod.json`:"
msgstr "事前ビルド設定スクリプトは、native ターゲット向けプログラミングを支援するために追加されました。このようなスクリプトを使うには、`moon.mod.json` にスクリプトを追加します："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:621
msgid ""
"options(\n"
"  \"--moonbit-unstable-prebuild\": \"<path/to/build-script>\",\n"
")\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:628
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"--moonbit-unstable-prebuild\": \"<path/to/build-script>\"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:636
msgid ""
"The path is a relative path from the root of the project. The script may "
"either be a JavaScript script (with extension `.js`, `.cjs`, `.mjs`) "
"executed with `node`, or a Python script (with extension `.py`) executed "
"with `python3` or `python`."
msgstr ""
"パスはプロジェクトルートからの相対パスです。スクリプトには、`node` で実行される JavaScript スクリプト（拡張子 `.js`、`.cjs`、`.mjs`）か、"
"`python3` または `python` で実行される Python スクリプト（拡張子 `.py`）を指定できます。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:641
msgid "Input"
msgstr "入力"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:643
msgid ""
"The script will be provided with a JSON with the structure of "
"`BuildScriptEnvironment` from standard input stream (stdin):"
msgstr "スクリプトには、標準入力ストリーム（stdin）から `BuildScriptEnvironment` 構造の JSON が渡されます："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:646
msgid ""
"/** Represents the environment a build script receives */\n"
"interface BuildScriptEnvironment {\n"
"  env: Record<string, string>\n"
"  paths: Paths\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"interface BuildInfo {\n"
"  /** The target info for the build script currently being run. */\n"
"  host: TargetInfo\n"
"  /** The target info for the module being built. */\n"
"  target: TargetInfo\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"interface TargetInfo {\n"
"  /** The actual backend we're using, e.g. `wasm32`, `wasmgc`, `js`, `c`,"
" `llvm` */\n"
"  kind: string // TargetBackend\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:666
msgid "Output"
msgstr "出力"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:668
msgid ""
"The script is expected to print a JSON string in its standard output "
"stream (stdout) with the structure of `BuildScriptOutput`:"
msgstr "スクリプトは、標準出力ストリーム（stdout）に `BuildScriptOutput` 構造の JSON 文字列を出力することが期待されます："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:671
msgid ""
"interface BuildScriptOutput {\n"
"  /** Build variables */\n"
"  vars?: Record<string, string>\n"
"  /** Configurations to linking */\n"
"  link_configs?: LinkConfig[]\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"interface LinkConfig {\n"
"  /** The name of the package to configure */\n"
"  package: string\n"
"\n"
"  /** Link flags that needs to be propagated to dependents\n"
"   *\n"
"   * Reference: `cargo::rustc-link-arg=FLAG` */\n"
"  link_flags?: string\n"
"\n"
"  /** Libraries that need linking, propagated to dependents\n"
"   *\n"
"   * Reference: `cargo::rustc-link-lib=LIB` */\n"
"  link_libs?: string[]\n"
"\n"
"  /** Paths that needs to be searched during linking, propagated to "
"dependents\n"
"   *\n"
"   * Reference: `cargo::rustc-link-search=[KIND=]PATH` */\n"
"  link_search_paths?: string[]\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:700
msgid "Build variables"
msgstr "ビルド変数"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:702
msgid ""
"You may use the variables emitted in the `vars` fields in the native "
"linking arguments in `moon.pkg` as `${build.<var_name>}`."
msgstr "`vars` フィールドに出力された変数は、`moon.pkg` の native リンク引数内で `${build.<var_name>}` として使用できます。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:705
msgid "For example, if your build script outputs:"
msgstr "例えば、ビルドスクリプトが次を出力する場合："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:707
msgid "{ \"vars\": { \"CC\": \"gcc\" } }\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:711
msgid "and your `moon.pkg` is structured like:"
msgstr "そして `moon.pkg` が次のような構成の場合："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:713
msgid "moon.pkg"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:713
msgid ""
"options(\n"
"  link: {\n"
"    \"native\": {\n"
"      \"cc\": \"${build.CC}\",\n"
"    },\n"
"  },\n"
")\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:718
msgid "It will be transformed into"
msgstr "次のように変換されます"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/module.md:720
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"link\": {\n"
"    \"native\": {\n"
"      \"cc\": \"gcc\"\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

